  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>MOS 36-Item Short Form Health Survey</measure>
    <time_frame>up to 4 weeks</time_frame>
    <description>The SF-36 - a patient-reported survey of patient health - consists of eight scaled scores, which are the weighted sums of the questions in their section. Each scale is directly transformed into a 0-100 scale on the assumption that each question carries equal weight.</description>
